---
/**
 * Atelier 工作室介紹頁（/atelier）
 * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
 * 區塊組成：Hero 標題 → What we do 雙語介紹 → What we refuse 拒絕宣言
 *
 * 怎麼設定：
 *   ▸ 改大標題「A studio, not a shop.」→ 改 .atelier-hero__display 內的文字
 *   ▸ 改中文標題「一間工作室，不是花店。」→ 改 .atelier-hero__tc
 *   ▸ 改「What we do」段落 → 改 .atelier-statement 內的兩欄 <p>
 *   ▸ 加/減「拒絕」項目 → 改 .atelier-refusal__list 內的 <span> 區塊
 *   ▸ 拒絕項目左側 bark 縱線 → .atelier-refusal__list span { border-left }
 */
import SitePage from '../../components/SitePage.astro';
import EyebrowRule from '../../components/EyebrowRule.astro';
---
<SitePage
  title="Atelier · 工作室 · SERENITY FLOWER"
  description="An atelier of installation art, wedding design, and seasonal florals from Taipei."
  active="Atelier"
>
  <section class="atelier-hero">
    <EyebrowRule en="Atelier · 工作室" />
    <h1 class="atelier-hero__display">A studio, not a shop.</h1>
    <p class="atelier-hero__tc">一間工作室，不是花店。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="atelier-statement">
    <div class="atelier-statement__col">
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>SERENITY FLOWER operates at the intersection of <em>floristry</em>, <em>installation art</em>, and <em>architectural space-making</em>. We treat plant material as a structural medium, not as decorative filler.</p>
      <p>Three integrated tracks — installation, wedding design, seasonal florals — each composed with the same vocabulary: volume, skeleton, circulation, void.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="atelier-statement__col">
      <h2>我們做什麼</h2>
      <p>靜謐花間，是一個橫跨花藝、裝置藝術、與空間建構的工作室。我們把植物當作結構媒材，而非裝飾的填充。</p>
      <p>三條交織的服務線——裝置藝術、婚禮佈置、節慶花禮——共用同一套語彙：量體、骨架、動線、留白。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="atelier-refusal">
    <EyebrowRule en="What we refuse" tc="我們拒絕" />
    <p class="atelier-refusal__list">
      <span>The maximalist floral abundance of the wedding industry default. ／<br/>婚禮產業預設的繁複堆疊。</span>
      <span>The generic line-drawn florals and scripted wordmarks of the “boutique florist” default. ／<br/>「精品花店」常見的細線插畫與草寫字標。</span>
      <span>Ornament for ornament's sake. ／<br/>為裝飾而裝飾。</span>
    </p>
  </section>
</SitePage>

<style>
  .atelier-hero { padding: var(--s-9) 0 var(--s-7); }
  .atelier-hero__display {
    font-family: var(--font-display-en);
    font-size: var(--fs-display-2);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--lh-display);
    letter-spacing: var(--tr-display);
    margin: var(--s-4) 0 0;
  }
  .atelier-hero__tc {
    font-family: var(--font-display-tc);
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: var(--s-2) 0 0;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .atelier-statement {
    padding: var(--s-9) 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--s-8);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-10);
  }
  .atelier-statement h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display-en);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    color: var(--bark);
  }
  .atelier-statement em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink); }
  .atelier-statement__col p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--ink); max-width: none; }
  .atelier-statement__col:last-child p { font-family: var(--font-body-tc); line-height: var(--lh-tc-body); }

  .atelier-refusal { padding: var(--s-9) 0 var(--s-10); border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-10); }
  .atelier-refusal__list {
    margin-top: var(--s-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--s-5);
    font-family: var(--font-body-en);
    font-size: var(--fs-h4);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .atelier-refusal__list span {
    padding-left: var(--s-5);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bark);
  }
  /* Tablet ≤ 960：雙語介紹改單欄 */
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .atelier-hero { padding: var(--s-8) 0 var(--s-6); }
    .atelier-hero__display { font-size: 56px; }
    .atelier-hero__tc { font-size: 28px; }
    .atelier-statement {
      padding: var(--s-8) 0;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--s-6);
    }
    .atelier-refusal { padding: var(--s-8) 0 var(--s-9); }
    .atelier-refusal__list { font-size: 18px; }
  }
  /* Mobile ≤ 640 */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .atelier-hero { padding: var(--s-7) 0 var(--s-5); }
    .atelier-hero__display { font-size: 42px; line-height: 1.06; }
    .atelier-hero__tc { font-size: 24px; }
    .atelier-statement { padding: var(--s-7) 0; gap: var(--s-5); }
    .atelier-statement h2 { font-size: 22px; }
    .atelier-statement__col p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; }
    .atelier-refusal__list { font-size: 16px; gap: var(--s-4); }
    .atelier-refusal__list span { padding-left: var(--s-4); }
  }
</style>
